将k8s的config文件配置到 ~/.kube目录下

```bash
~]# ls .kube/
cache  config  config.ghost  config.jyjt  config.office
```

查看pod的命令为

```bash
~]# kubectl --kubeconfig ~/.kube/config.jyjt get pods --all-namespaces  
~]# kubectl --kubeconfig ~/.kube/config.ghost get pods --all-namespaces  
~]# kubectl --kubeconfig ~/.kube/config.office get pods --all-namespaces  
```

### office-k8s

config.office

```
apiVersion: v1
clusters:
- cluster:
    certificate-authority-data: 
    server: https://10.230.7.20:6443
  name: kubernetes
contexts:
- context:
    cluster: kubernetes
    user: kubernetes-admin
  name: kubernetes-admin@kubernetes
current-context: kubernetes-admin@kubernetes
kind: Config
preferences: {}
users:
- name: kubernetes-admin
  user:
    client-certificate-data: 
    client-key-data: 
```
